        "subject": "LU-3401 tests: add version check codes into sanity test 27z",
        "message": "LU-3401 tests: add version check codes into sanity test 27z\n\nThis patch adds Lustre version check codes into sanity test 27z\nto make the test work with servers which do not contain the\nll_decode_filter_fid.c changes in the following patch:\n\nLustre-commit: b4cd56fc7c4365b89bc0494f4939f744f7a78175\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/6468\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes \\\nclientdistro=el6 serverdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nserverarch=x86_64 serverjob=lustre-b2_1 serverbuildno=191 \\\ntestlist=sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icaaa256c8a56a065b3b6306b0eacb099ef077252\n"
      },
